en-US.title: Anchor Health Connecticut - A Leader in LGBTQ Health
en-US.description: Anchor Health provides groundbreaking, radically inclusive, gender-affirming, and sex-positive care for the LGBTQ community, with a focus on transgender and gender diverse individuals. They offer a range of services such as primary care, behavioral health, sexual health, and HIV prevention with a holistic approach, striving to create a safe and understanding environment for queer individuals.
